                <p class="text-muted mt-1" style="font-size: small;">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle bg-cols"></i> LEGAL INFO: Online Order Service is
                    provided by Hungry4food.com a subsidiary of Noble Idea Solution LLC. Payment charged on your
                    credit card statement is payment to food and services purchased from your restaurant.
                    Charge-back fees applied for valid purchased will be responsibility of cardholder. Any Delivery
                    Charge is not a tip paid to your driver. Please reward your driver for awesomeness. Delivery
                    charge and tax may apply. Prices, participation, delivery area and charges may vary. Returned
                    checks, along with the state maximum allowable returned check fee, may be electronically
                    presented to your bank.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer__inner w-100 pt-1 row mt-3"></div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <p class="text-white mt-5 font-weight-bold footer__heading">
                    @(Model!=null? Model.title: "") 
                </p>

