                    doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi
                    architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo eni
                </p>

            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <p class="text-white mt-5 font-weight-bold footer__heading">
                    Quick links
                </p>
                <ul class="m-0 p-0">
                    <li class="mt-4">
                        <a href="#" class="text-white">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-2">
                        <a href="#" class="text-white">About</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-2">
                        <a href="#" class="text-white">Order Now</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-2">
                        <a href="#" class="text-white">Open Hours</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mt-2">
                        <a href="#" class="text-white">Reserve a Table</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <p class="text-white mt-5 font-weight-bold footer__heading">
                    FIND US
